trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlInputFile> control implements the <xref:System.Web.UI.IPostBackDataHandler> interface, which has two methods: <xref:System.Web.UI.IPostBackDataHandler.LoadPostData%2A?displayProperty=fullName> and <xref:System.Web.UI.IPostBackDataHandler.RaisePostDataChangedEvent%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlInputFile>valósít meg szabályozhatja a <xref:System.Web.UI.IPostBackDataHandler>felület, amely két módszer van: <xref:System.Web.UI.IPostBackDataHandler.LoadPostData%2A?displayProperty=fullName>és <xref:System.Web.UI.IPostBackDataHandler.RaisePostDataChangedEvent%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Web.UI.IPostBackDataHandler.RaisePostDataChangedEvent%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.IPostBackDataHandler.LoadPostData%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.IPostBackDataHandler> </xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlInputFile>

trans-unit.source: The LoadPostData method is called by the <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlInputFile.System%23Web%23UI%23IPostBackDataHandler%23RaisePostDataChangedEvent%2A> method and always returns `false`, indicating that the <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlInputFile> control's state is not managed by the ASP.NET page framework.
trans-unit.target: A kezelnie metódust a <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlInputFile.System%23Web%23UI%23IPostBackDataHandler%23RaisePostDataChangedEvent%2A>metódust, és mindig adja vissza `false`, jelző, amely a <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlInputFile>vezérlő állapota nem kezeli az ASP.NET-lapok keretrendszerének.</xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlInputFile> </xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlInputFile.System%23Web%23UI%23IPostBackDataHandler%23RaisePostDataChangedEvent%2A>

trans-unit.source: The LoadPostData method is used primarily by control developers extending the functionality of the <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlInputFile> control.
